<h2>Booking Confirmed 🎉</h2>

<p>Hi <%= @booking.guest_name %>,</p>

<p>Your booking has been successfully confirmed.</p>

<p><strong>Property:</strong> <%= @homestay.name %></p>
<p><strong>Dates:</strong> <%= @booking.check_in_date %> to <%= @booking.check_out_date %></p>
<p><strong>Guests:</strong> <%= @booking.number_of_guests %></p>
<p><strong>Total:</strong> <%= number_to_currency(@booking.total_price, unit: "₹", precision: (@booking.total_price.to_f % 1).zero? ? 0 : 2) %></p>

<p>We look forward to hosting you!</p>
